ens-jun-to-star-alongside-jackie-chan-tony-leung-in-the-shadows-edge-3830610">SEVENTEEN的Jun将与成龙、梁朝伟联袂主演的《影之边缘》</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
