所有物品和记忆都在大火中被毁。她当时写道：“我和我孩子们的家已经消失了。我们所有的东西都被烧毁了。求主怜悯。庆幸我们还有彼此。从头开始。我的心好沉重。”</p><p>现在，Jheń Aiko 和她的健康品牌 Jhenetics 向冒着生命危险扑灭洛杉矶五场连续大火的前线人员表示感谢。 Aiko 和 Jhenetics 为消防员提供免费按摩服务，并使用 Jhenetics 产品帮助消防员缓解压力和疼痛。</p><p> Aiko 和她的品牌<a href="https://www.instagram.com/jheneticsbyjheneaiko/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 Instagram 上写道</a>：“感谢我们的急救人员，他们在远离家人的日子里不知疲倦地工作来保护我们。我们希望这一小小的感激之情能够在这些漫长的轮班期间发挥作用。”</p><p>许多音乐家在火灾后挺身而出，为受影响的社区提供帮助。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-foundation-announces-2-5million-donation-to-la-wildfire-relief-3828303">碧昂斯 (Beyoncé) 的 BeyGOOD 基金会已捐赠 250 万美元，</a>用于帮助洛杉矶山火的救灾工作。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">帕丽斯·希尔顿还为因火灾而流离失所的家庭发起了一项基金</a>，承诺捐款 10 万美元，并承诺匹配最多 10 万美元的捐款。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-spent-birthday-making-meals-for-families-hit-by-la-wildfires-3829226">戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl) 也在生日那天为受影响的家庭做饭</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3828876" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828876" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828876" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Hollywood-Wildfires.jpg" alt="好莱坞野火" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Hollywood-Wildfires.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Hollywood-Wildfires-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Hollywood-Wildfires-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Hollywood-Wildfires-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Hollywood-Wildfires-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Hollywood-Wildfires-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828876" class="wp-caption-text">一名消防员在洛杉矶扑救野火 图片来源：Mario Tama/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>美国-墨西哥乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/american-mexican-fuerza-regida-rent-entire-hotel-shelter-victims-wildfires-3828174">Fuerza Regida 将整个酒店出租一​​周，为逃离山火的 50 个家庭提供庇护</a>。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-joins-fireaid-benefit-concert-for-la-wildfire-relief-3830217"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-urges-brands-gifting-her-clothing-to-instead-donate-it-to-those-affected-by-horrific-la-wildfires-3828185">Charli XCX 呼吁品牌赠送她的衣服“将它们送给真正需要它的人”。</a>随后，她分享了造型师 Lana Jay Lackey 组织的衣物捐赠活动的细节，并敦促其他人与她一起捐赠。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">阿丽亚娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a> 、比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 等人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">对野火造成的“令人心碎”的破坏做出了反应</a>，为需要帮助的人分享资源链接。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界的成员也向<i>《NME》</i>表示，他们受到了严重打击</a>，许多场馆、工作室和艺术家都受到了火灾的影响。</p><p>此外，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-joins-fireaid-benefit-concert-for-la-wildfire-relief-3830217">Billie Eilish、Stevie Nicks、Olivia Rodrigo、Green Day、No Doubt 等在内的音乐家已宣布将在 1 月 30 日即将举行的 FireAid 慈善音乐会上进行表演</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jhene-aiko-sponsors-massages-for-firefighters-of-la-wildfires-3830598">Jheń Aiko 赞助洛杉矶野火消防员按摩的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
娱乐界对唐纳德·特朗普的“双性”政策做出反应：“做真正的自己的权利至关重要” https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-donald-trumps-two-gender-policy-the-right-to-be-who-we-truly-are-is-至关重要的-3830582？u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=娱乐世界对唐纳德·特朗普的两性政策做出反应，成为我们真正的人的权利至关重要Surej SinghTue, 21 Jan 2025 04:45:13 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsTV NewsDonald TrumpPolitics https://www.nme.com/?p=3830582 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>美国总统裁定美国只承认两种性别：男性和女性</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-donald-trumps-two-gender-policy-the-right-to-be-who-we-truly-are-is-vital-3830582">娱乐界对唐纳德·特朗普的“双性别”政策做出反应：“做真正的自己的权利至关重要”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ariana-grande-aurora-donald-trump@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>总统<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/social-media-reacts-to-donald-trump-declaring-that-america-will-only-recognise-two-sexes-all-those-years-of-progression-gone-in-an-instant-3830538">规定美利坚合众国将只承认两种性别，即男性和女性</a>——看看名人对以下政策的看法。</p><p>昨天（1月20日），唐纳德·特朗普第二次宣誓就任美国总统。总统在就职演说中宣布：“从今天起，美国政府的官方政策是只有两种性别：男性和女性。”</p><p>虽然特朗普最初似乎混淆了“性别”和“社会性别”这两个术语，但他的政府澄清说，总统将签署一项行政命令，仅承认两种性别——男性和女性——并宣布它们不能改变，并且联邦雇主需要使用性别一词，而不是性别。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830543" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830543" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830543" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Donald-Trump-Photo-by-Greg-Nash-_-POOL-_-AFP-Photo-by-GREG-NASH_POOL_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="唐纳德·特朗普" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Donald-Trump-Photo-by-Greg-Nash-_-POOL-_-AFP-Photo-by-GREG-NASH_POOL_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Donald-Trump-Photo-by-Greg-Nash-_-POOL-_-AFP-Photo-by-GREG-NASH_POOL_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Donald-Trump-Photo-by-Greg-Nash-_-POOL-_-AFP-Photo-by-GREG-NASH_POOL_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Donald-Trump-Photo-by-Greg-Nash-_-POOL-_-AFP-Photo-by-GREG-NASH_POOL_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Donald-Trump-Photo-by-Greg-Nash-_-POOL-_-AFP-Photo-by-GREG-NASH_POOL_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Donald-Trump-Photo-by-Greg-Nash-_-POOL-_-AFP-Photo-by-GREG-NASH_POOL_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830543" class="wp-caption-text">唐纳德·特朗普 – 图片来源：Greg Nash/POOL/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>作为参考，性别是指人类的生物学特征，而社会性别是指社会建构的男性和女性特征。</p><p>自他宣布这一政策以来，一些名人已经在社交媒体上分享了他们对该政策的看法。在就职之前，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德</a>分享了一系列 Instagram 故事，强调 LGBTQIA+ 群体在竞选期间面临特朗普政府及其支持者的困境。</p><p>特朗普发表政策声明后，她<a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/arianagrande/3549916426321198595/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 Instagram Stories 上分享了一篇转发文章，内容如下</a>：“让我们明确一点：酷儿和跨性别者在唐纳德·特朗普之前就已经存在，并且在他死后仍将继续存在。你是否希望我们存在并不重要，重要的是我们确实存在这个简单的事实。太阳并不关心你是否签署了一项行政命令，让它每天早上停止升起。它只会继续上升。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aurora">奥罗拉</a>(Aurora) 公开自己的双性恋身份，<a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/auroramusic/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">她在 Instagram Stories 上向她的变性追随者表示慰藉</a>：“致我所有的[变性]朋友、同事以及美国变性群体中所有美丽的成员，还没有很高兴见到。我对你们自己的政府的失败深感悲痛。”</p><p>奥罗拉继续说道：“被看到和听到的权利确实很重要。做真正的自己的权利至关重要。我想让你知道我的心与你同在。我对世界运行方式的担忧也加深了。对未知的恐惧和对不同事物的恐惧并不是我们与生俱来的。学到了。”</p><p> “我希望再次提醒我们，爱的力量和人民的力量。愿我们永远不会停止，以我们谦卑的请求——自由地表达我们是谁，以及我们想要如何生活，”奥罗拉总结道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830583" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830583" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830583" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/donald-trump@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/donald-trump@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/donald-trump@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont