日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/whitesnake-and-thin-lizzy-guitarist-john-sykes-has-died-aged-65-3830586">Whitesnake 和Thin Lizzy 吉他手John Sykes 去世，享年65 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
